#if-else statement
check = "Hamburger"
if check == False:
    print("It is false")
elif check == "Hamburger":
    print("Yeayyy,burger")
elif check =="Yo":
    print("Holla")
else:
    print("It is actually equal to True")
Yeayyy,burger
-klu sama dngn check tu, dia akan print apa yg dicheck tu. Klu x..dia print else
